{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji28.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给粟济世的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给栗济世\"的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1950年5月7日）济世先生："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一月一日惠书敬悉，极为感谢。征粮弊病甚多，政府已有令纠正，未知实际效果如何？剿匪取宽大政策期收速效，根治则有待于土地制度之改革。先生如有所见，尚祈随时赐示为盼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺颂健吉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五○年五月七日[1]粟济世，毛泽东在湖南省立第一师范学校读书时的同学。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":5,"day":7}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":344,"page_end":344},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}